    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Description:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Shoot &amp; Neon</i> is a laid-back multiplayer FPS where you and your (possibly too many) friends try to survive endless waves of neon bean-shaped enemies. It’s easy to jump in, hard to keep up — and even harder to stop laughing when things go off the rails.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up upgrades, level up, and fight through increasing chaos as the enemy count skyrockets. There’s no real end — just an ever-growing mess of bullets, glowing blobs, and last-minute dodges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or with others (stable with up to 6 players — but hey, there’s technically no hard limit). Whether you’re chasing a high score, unlocking all 100 achievements, or just vibing in the neon madness, <i>Shoot &amp; Neon</i> keeps things light, fun, and a little ridiculous. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Chaos</strong><br>The longer you survive, the messier it gets. Enemies multiply fast — good luck keeping track.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352710/extras/f3dba9a3f89229d50609dcac92e4dfe0.poster.avif?t=1749324097\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352710/extras/f3dba9a3f89229d50609dcac92e4dfe0.webm?t=1749324097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352710/extras/f3dba9a3f89229d50609dcac92e4dfe0.mp4?t=1749324097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple Upgrade System</strong><br>Pick up upgrades or choose one when you level up. Get stronger, stay alive longer.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352710/extras/feaf737733aeb73239ea262f42b9c8e2.poster.avif?t=1749324097\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352710/extras/feaf737733aeb73239ea262f42b9c8e2.webm?t=1749324097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352710/extras/feaf737733aeb73239ea262f42b9c8e2.mp4?t=1749324097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer Mayhem (No Player Limit?) <br>Team up with friends to survive wave after wave of glowing enemies.<br>Officially stable with 6. But there’s no cap — add more players and embrace the madness.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352710/extras/ff3166d233696dc69e13f84571dfc399.poster.avif?t=1749324097\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352710/extras/ff3166d233696dc69e13f84571dfc399.webm?t=1749324097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352710/extras/ff3166d233696dc69e13f84571dfc399.mp4?t=1749324097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100 Achievements to Unlock</strong><br>The real endgame. Can you survive long enough (and be lucky enough) to catch 'em all?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352710/extras/889bb03ff03bf359e6d0a1747a17ddfb.poster.avif?t=1749324097\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352710/extras/889bb03ff03bf359e6d0a1747a17ddfb.webm?t=1749324097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352710/extras/889bb03ff03bf359e6d0a1747a17ddfb.mp4?t=1749324097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Global &amp; Friends Leaderboards</strong><br>Prove your bean is better. Or just flex on your co-op buddies.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352710/extras/eee9caee5feb5417998ec4c5c827c2db.poster.avif?t=1749324097\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352710/extras/eee9caee5feb5417998ec4c5c827c2db.webm?t=1749324097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352710/extras/eee9caee5feb5417998ec4c5c827c2db.mp4?t=1749324097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
